Invocation Name: find a bike
des:
You can use this skill to find out how many bikes and docks are at any given Divvy Station in Chicago.

Ask Alexa "How many Divvys are at Millennium Park", and she'll tell you how many bikes and open docks are at the station. Try it with your closest station!

Divvy is operated by Motivate for Chicago Department of Transportation. This skill is not affiliated with Motivate or Chicago Department of Transportation.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
